label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"病毒性关节炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":13,"text":"呼肠孤病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":19,"end":24,"text":"常见传染病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":16,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 病毒性关节炎是由呼肠孤病毒引起鸡的一种常见传染病。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"病毒性关节炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"肉仔鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":38,"end":41,"text":"蛋小鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 病毒性关节炎可水平传播，也可垂直传播，4～7周龄肉仔鸡最易感，3～10周龄的蛋小鸡亦易发生。

label: [{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":8,"end":15,"text":"后肢跗关节肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":21,"text":"滑膜炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"滑膜出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"腱鞘炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"腱鞘肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":44,"text":"腓肠肌断裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"断裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":55,"text":"腓肠肌及其肌腱出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":53,"end":55,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":56,"end":62,"text":"周围组织肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":65,"end":71,"text":"关节软骨出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":69,"end":71,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":72,"end":74,"text":"糜烂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":75,"end":81,"text":"糜烂逐渐扩大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":83,"end":87,"text":"侵害骨质","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":89,"end":93,"text":"骨膜增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":91,"end":93,"text":"增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":118,"end":122,"text":"站起困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":123,"end":125,"text":"跛行","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":128,"end":133,"text":"跗关节僵硬","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":131,"end":133,"text":"僵硬","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":141,"end":143,"text":"瘫痪","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":152,"end":156,"text":"庭竭死亡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":96,"end":102,"text":"病毒性关节炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":104,"end":108,"text":"腱滑膜炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":109,"end":115,"text":"病毒性腱鞘炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":116,"end":118,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":8,"end":13,"text":"后肢跗关节","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"滑膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"腱鞘","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":39,"end":42,"text":"腓肠肌","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":46,"end":49,"text":"腓肠肌","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"肌腱","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":65,"end":69,"text":"关节软骨","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":89,"end":91,"text":"骨膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":128,"end":131,"text":"跗关节","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 主要症状是：病鸡后肢跗关节肿胀，引起滑膜炎，滑膜出血，腱鞘炎，腱鞘肿胀，严重时腓肠肌断裂，使腓肠肌及其肌腱出血，周围组织肿胀，继而关节软骨出血，糜烂，糜烂逐渐扩大，并侵害骨质，使骨膜增厚，所以病毒性关节炎又叫腱滑膜炎或病毒性腱鞘炎。病鸡站起困难，跛行，甚至跗关节僵硬，不能活动，造成瘫痪，最后因采食困难而庭竭死亡。

label: [{"start":5,"end":13,"text":"跗关节滑液膜出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"淡青黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"渗出物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"脓性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":42,"end":47,"text":"腓肠肌断裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":45,"end":47,"text":"断裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":52,"end":55,"text":"青紫色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":11,"text":"跗关节滑液膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"关节腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":42,"end":45,"text":"腓肠肌","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 剖检时还见跗关节滑液膜出血，关节腔中积有少量淡青黄色或带血色的渗出物，有时可为脓性。腓肠肌断裂时，外观显青紫色。

label: [{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"皮下注射","labels":["control"]},{"start":22,"end":31,"text":"禽呼肠孤病毒Po苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 防制措施：参考免疫程序：1～7日龄首免，选用禽呼肠孤病毒Po苗皮下注射；

label: [{"start":11,"end":24,"text":"禽呼肠孤病毒S-1733苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":39,"end":51,"text":"禽呼肠孤病毒S-1733","labels":["drug"]},{"start":52,"end":58,"text":"S-2408","labels":["drug"]},{"start":59,"end":65,"text":"C08灭活苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":65,"end":72,"text":"皮下或肌内注射","labels":["control"]}]
text: 8～10周龄二免，选用禽呼肠孤病毒S-1733苗饮水；18～20周龄三免，选用禽呼肠孤病毒S-1733,S-2408或C08灭活苗皮下或肌内注射。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"抗菌药物","labels":["drug"]},{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"红霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"选用抗菌药物预防","labels":["control"]}]
text: 选用抗菌药物预防或治疗继发感染，如红霉素按0.1%～0.2%饮水，连饮3～5天；

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"环丙沙星","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 环丙沙星按每升水加50～100毫克，饮水，连饮3～5天。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"注意消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"碱液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"碘液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"甲醛液","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 加强饲养管理，注意消毒，常用碱液、碘液、甲醛液。
